            "text": "III. Atipia de significado indeterminado\\N(AUS/FLUS)",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "• Riesgo malignidad: 5-15%",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "text": "• Conducta:",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "• Repetir PAAF o pruebas moleculares.",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "IV. Neoplasia folicular o sospecha de\\Nneoplasia folicular (FN/SFN)",
